1
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:14,700
Doctor.

2
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,000
How is my brother?

3
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,240
He has a graze on his arm,

4
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:18,160
and a puncture wound to the abdomen.

5
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:20,820
But luckily, it didn't hit any internal organs.

6
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:46,850
Come out.

7
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,120
Where is the secret recipe?

8
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:58,400
I searched Zhang Qi.

9
00:00:58,600 --> 00:01:00,000
There was nothing on him.

10
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,760
Was there nothing?

11
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:04,290
Or was it never on him at all?

12
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,080
Commander.

13
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,440
What do you mean by that?

14
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,280
Xiao Zhang is your trusted aide.

15
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,960
How could you not know what he was doing?

16
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:15,720
To others, the secret recipe is just a piece of paper.

17
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:17,720
But only you know its value.

18
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,280
I heard

19
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,480
you've been very close with the Yao family recently.

20
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,410
How much did Old Master Yao pay you?

21
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,500
Commander.

22
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,560
I didn't!

23
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,480
I've followed you for so long.

24
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,880
How could I betray you?

25
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,220
It doesn't matter.

26
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,460
Someone framed me!

27
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,360
Commander, someone framed me!

28
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:36,080
But you hurt Qingzhou.

29
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,680
I can't spare you.

30
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,720
No, Commander.

31
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:39,560
It was him.

32
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:40,840
He was trying to save a woman.

33
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,240
I didn't mean to.

34
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:41,680
I...

35
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:02,960
Have a drink.

36
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,780
Song Qingzhou.

37
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,720
Cheer up.

38
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,810
We planned this for so long.

39
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,920
We finally got rid of that adjutant.

40
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,960
That kid never would have guessed

41
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:21,560
that we paid top dollar to turn Zhang Qi.

42
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:24,290
Zhang Qi took the risk to steal the secret recipe.

43
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,240
Incredible.

44
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,360
Money talks.

45
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:32,329
The adjutant was just a dog following orders.

46
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,980
The real targets of my revenge

47
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,520
are still alive and kicking.

48
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,480
Be patient.

49
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:45,010
It's back with its rightful owner.

50
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,690
This secret recipe is fake.

51
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:54,079
We went through so much trouble to get it.

52
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,240
How do you know it's fake?

53
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,920
Although I haven't seen

54
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,400
my family's secret recipe,

55
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,160
the medicated soap made from this

56
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,200
will likely have the opposite effect.

57
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:03,680
Master Zhu poured his life's work

58
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,560
into this recipe.

59
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,080
He fought hard to keep it from foreigners.

60
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,080
But now,

61
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:11,000
it's completely lost.

62
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,200
Luoli.

63
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:13,920
This is the Zhu family heirloom necklace.

64
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,560
Keep it safe and close to you.

65
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,960
I know where it is.

66
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,200
Even if they turn the Zhu house

67
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,240
upside down,

68
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,620
they'll still only find the fake recipe.

69
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:29,079
The recipe must be hidden there.

70
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:29,640
Where?

71
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:33,170
I left a family jade pendant at the Song house.

72
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,240
You mean,

73
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,360
the recipe is hidden in the most dangerous place?

74
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,090
Which is also the safest place.

75
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,920
But I need to find it soon.

76
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:43,400
I'm afraid Song Huainan will discover the secret inside.

77
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,600
At least we have a lead.

78
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,640
What about the dagger that killed my father?

79
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,800
Have you found anything?

80
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,600
I found a few things.

81
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:51,290
Rumor has it the Song brothers have it.

82
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,530
But as for exactly whose hands it's in,

83
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,370
I don't know.

84
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,940
That's up to you to verify.

85
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,880
Song Huainan

86
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,920
rarely carries a dagger.

87
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:04,000
Could it be Song Qingzhou?

88
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:05,880
I'll give you a quote for free,

89
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:08,080
a famous saying in the detective world.

90
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,520
When you have eliminated the impossible,

91
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,580
whatever remains,

92
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,120
however improbable,

93
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,040
must be the truth.

94
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,530
What are you doing here?

95
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:45,440
Still pushing yourself so hard while injured?

96
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,640
Thanks for saving me.

97
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,760
I'm fine.

98
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,960
I've pretty much recovered.

99
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,290
Yao Shengsheng,

100
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:02,440
don't you think you owe me an explanation?

101
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,970
Why were you there that day?

102
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,600
I saved you,

103
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,240
and you want an explanation?

104
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,440
You're treating my kindness like dirt.

105
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,920
No,

106
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,000
I'm just curious.

107
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,120
Normally,

108
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,880
you shouldn't have been in a place like that.

109
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:19,210
Do I need to explain my whereabouts to you?

110
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:22,040
I guess I shouldn't have worried about you.

111
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,240
Song Qingzhou.

112
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,760
Regarding what happened to the Zhu family that night,

113
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,360
were you involved?

114
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:37,159
It's time for the Yao and Song families

115
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,640
to switch places.

116
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,520
It's just Johnson.

117
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,360
Look how worried you are.

118
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,240
Song Huainan has an army.

119
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,760
I'm afraid even Johnson can't control him.

120
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,840
If the Song family

121
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,240
hadn't gone too far,

122
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,200
would I have taken this step?

123
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,320
When we destroyed the Zhu family together,

124
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,240
they promised me that

125
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,400
the secret recipe would be mine if found.

126
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,460
But what happened?

127
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:04,940
They're using this secret recipe to keep me under their thumb.

128
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,690
So I'll find a foreigner to keep them in check.

129
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,280
Marshal Song.

130
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:13,560
The Yao family wants to collaborate with Ambassador Johnson.

131
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,960
They are just merchants.

132
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,840
It is already beneath the Song family to work with them.

133
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:20,520
Yet they have the nerve to try and walk all over us.

134
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,120
They don't know their place.

135
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:40,340
Keep your supporting hand as steady as possible

136
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,120
to improve your shooting accuracy.

137
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,560
You've got good form.

138
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,730
Once I set my mind to something,

139
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,490
there's nothing I can't do.

140
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,810
That's determination.

141
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,410
Let's put it to the test.

142
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:12,690
Brother.

143
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,400
She's just a novice.

144
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,640
There's no need to test her, is there?

145
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,640
She's your student.

146
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,170
Don't you have faith in her?

147
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,360
But shooting targets is boring.

148
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:22,700
Shoot an apple.

149
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,720
Qingzhou.

150
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,120
Go over there.

151
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:27,810
Brother.

152
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,440
We're just playing.

153
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,540
Go stand there.

154
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,600
Song Huainan.

155
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,640
Testing like this...

156
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,700
what if I...

157
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,170
Yao Shengsheng.

158
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:46,580
Our military academy doesn't keep useless people.

159
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,480
If you don't even have the guts for this,

160
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,980
I suggest you leave now

161
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:53,040
and go back to being a pampered miss.

162
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,780
Raise your gun.

163
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,100
Straighten your arms.

164
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:57,880
Legs apart.

165
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,880
Focus on the target.

166
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,000
Don't miss.

167
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,560
When you think you're ready,

168
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:19,600
just shoot.

169
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,840
Don't tell me you can't bear to do it.

170
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,039
Fire.
